'''超級航空母艦'''（{{lang-en|'''supercarrier'''}}）是形容目前最大的[[航空母艦|航空母艦]]級別的非正式名詞，二戰後通常是指排水量在75,000噸以上的航空母艦<ref>David Miller and Lindsay Peacock, ''Carriers: The Men and the Machines'' (London and New York: Salamander, 1991), p. 7: "There are four main types of carrier in service today. Largest of these are the super-carriers displacing over 75,000 tons; the U.S. Navy currently has fourteen, the Soviet Navy one."</ref>。[[美國海軍|美國海軍]]擁有大部分這種級別的軍艦<ref>[http://www.cbsnews.com/stories/2010/05/21/opinion/main6506170.shtml Putting the Pentagon on a Recessionary Diet]</ref>，其他國家的航艦則相對较小，中大型航艦排水量40,000噸-75,000噸（如[[法國海軍|法國海軍]]的[[戴高樂號航空母艦|戴高樂號航空母艦]]），而[[輕型航空母艦|輕型航空母艦]]則在40,000噸以下（如[[意大利海軍|意大利海軍]]的[[加富尔號航空母艦|加富尔號航空母艦]]）。「超級航空母艦」也是目前世界上排水量最大的軍艦。美國和中國是僅有的能建造並擁有超級航母的國家。

==歷史==
超級航空母艦的說法最早起於1938年，由《[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]》用於形容英國海軍的[[皇家方舟号航空母舰_(1937年)|皇家方舟号航空母舰]]<ref>{{citation | contribution= Reich's Cruise Ships Held Potential Plane Carriers | title = The New York Times | date = May 1, 1938 | page = 32 | url = http://query.nytimes.com/search/sitesearch?query=%22Britain%27s+new+super-carrier%2C+the+Ark+Royal%22&date_select=full&srchst=cse}}.</ref>，其長662英呎、排水量22,000噸，設計可搭載72架飛機<ref>"The Ark Royal Launched.  Most Up-To-Date Carrier.  Aircraft In The Fleet", ''[[The_Times|The Times]]'' (14 April 1937), p. 11.</ref><ref>{{Cite book| last= Rossiter | first= Mike | title = Ark Royal: the life, death and rediscovery of the legendary Second World War aircraft carrier | url= https://archive.org/details/arkroyallifedeat0000ross |origyear=2006 |edition=2nd |year=2007 |publisher=Corgi Books |location=London | isbn = 978-0552153690 |oclc= 81453068 | pages = [https://archive.org/details/arkroyallifedeat0000ross/page/48 48]–51}}</ref>。1943年，其地位被美國45,000噸的[[中途島級航空母艦|中途島級航空母艦]]所取代，作為27,000噸的[[艾塞克斯級航空母艦|艾塞克斯級]]的強化型<ref>John G Norris, "World's Largest Warships: Three 45,000-Ton Carriers For Bombers Ordered by Navy", ''[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]]'' (23 October 1943), p. 1.</ref>。二戰後，超級航空母艦的地位交給了[[美國號航空母艦|美國號]]以及[[福萊斯特級航空母艦|福萊斯特級]]<ref>"Va. Firm Gets Giant Carrier Building Job.  65,000-Ton Warship Will Be Largest in Postwar Program", ''[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]]'' (8 August 1948), p. 3.</ref>。福萊斯特級排水量為60,000噸級，而在滿載狀態下航行則有75,000噸<ref>{{Cite book| last= Donald | first = David |coauthors = Daniel J March |title= Carrier Aviation Air Power Directory |year= 2001 |publisher= AIRtime Publishing |location = Norwalk, CT |isbn= 1-880588-43-9 |pages =77 }}</ref>，並被美國新聞界認為是當代標準下真正的第一艘「超級航空母艦」<ref>{{Cite book | format = PDF | last = MacDonald | first = Scot | title = Evolution of Aircraft Carriers | publisher = US Government Printing Office | date = 1964-02-01 | location = Washington, DC |url = |doi = |isbn = |id= | page = 69 | chapter= 14 | chapterurl= http://www.history.navy.mil/download/car-14.pdf | quote = The versatility of the current US carrier fleet is largely due to the operation of what the press has labeled 'super-carriers,' heavy duty aircraft carriers of the size, power, and potency of the Forrestals and the nuclear-powered Enterprise.}}</ref>，而同樣級別的[[美國號航空母艦|美國號]]則被取消建造，引發了「[[海軍上將叛亂事件|海軍上將叛亂事件]]」。

其他國家方面，蘇聯在[[冷戰|冷戰]]末期曾建造[[烏里揚諾夫斯克號航空母艦|烏里揚諾夫斯克號航空母艦]]，其為80,000噸級，也是蘇聯最大的航艦，但在完成40％的情況下因後冷戰時期的軍費縮減而於1991年取消工程。英國長期使用三艘輕型的[[无敌级航空母舰|无敌级航空母舰]]，而後回歸傳統路線建造大型航空母艦-[[伊莉莎白女王級航空母艦|伊莉莎白女王級]]，其為65,000噸級，法國同樣也計畫在同一平台建造新型航艦-{{le|二號航空母艦|French aircraft carrier PA2}}，約為75,000噸級，這兩種航艦都被英國媒體與國會議員稱之「超級航空母艦」<ref>[http://www.publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm200203/cmordbk1/30908w01.htm House of Commons Written Questions for Answer, 8 September 2003]</ref><ref>[http://www.publications.parliament.uk/pa/ld200607/ldhansrd/text/70315-0009.htm  House of Lords, 15 March 2007].</ref><ref>[http://www.publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm200708/cmhansrd/cm080617/text/80617w0014.htm House of Commons Written Answers for 17 June 2008]</ref><ref>[http://www.publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm200607/cmselect/cmscotaf/943/7071703.htm Select Committee on Scottish Affairs Minutes of Evidence, Examination of Witnesses (Questions 1–19), 17 July 2007]</ref><ref name="supercarrier">{{Cite news| title = Hoon to confirm ‘supercarrier’| url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk/1401764.stm| publisher = [[BBC_News|BBC News]]|date= 2001-06-22| accessdate = 2008-12-23}}</ref><ref name="Go ahead">{{Cite news| title = Go-ahead given for work to start on supercarriers| url = http://www.portsmouth.co.uk/hands-off-our-base/Goahead-given-for-work-to.4099975.jp| work = [[The_News_(Portsmouth)|Portsmouth News]]| date = 2008-05-20| accessdate = 2008-12-23| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090122080439/http://www.portsmouth.co.uk/hands-off-our-base/Goahead-given-for-work-to.4099975.jp| archive-date = 2009-01-22| dead-url = yes}}</ref><ref name="VT">{{Cite news| title = VT at forefront of £3.9bn supercarrier project| url = http://www.portsmouth.co.uk/hands-off-our-base/VT-at-forefront-of-39bn.4100855.jp| work = [[The_News_(Portsmouth)|Portsmouth News]]| date = 2008-05-20| accessdate = 2008-12-23| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090122080708/http://www.portsmouth.co.uk/hands-off-our-base/VT-at-forefront-of-39bn.4100855.jp| archive-date = 2009-01-22| dead-url = yes}}</ref><ref name="Janes">{{Cite news| title = Navy (France), Navy Assessment | url = http://www.janes.com/articles/Janes-Sentinel-Security-Assessment-Western-Europe/Navy-France.html | publisher = '' Jane’s Sentinel Security Assessment—Western Europe ''|date=2008-12-03| accessdate = 2008-12-28}}</ref><ref name="Delayed">{{Cite news| title = Navy aircraft carriers delayed| url = http://www.thenorthernecho.co.uk/news/3969255.Navy_aircraft_carriers_delayed/| work = [[The_Northern_Echo|The Northern Echo]] |date=2008-12-11| accessdate = 2008-12-23}}</ref><ref name="Job concerns">{{Cite news| title = Job concerns as MoD proposes carrier delay| url = http://www.thecourier.co.uk/output/2008/12/12/newsstory12371214t0.asp| work = [[The_Courier|The Courier]]| date = 2008-12-12| accessdate = 2008-12-23| deadurl = yes| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081215100719/http://www.thecourier.co.uk/output/2008/12/12/newsstory12371214t0.asp| archivedate = 2008-12-15}}</ref><ref name = "Airfix">{{Cite news| title = The £4billion Airfix Kit: Behind-the-scenes at Britain's biggest warships| url = http://www.dailymail.co.uk/home/moslive/article-1100714/The-4billion-Airfix-Kit-Behind-scenes-Britains-biggest-warships.html| work = [[Daily_Mail|Daily Mail]]|date= 2008-05-28| accessdate = 2008-12-28 | location=London | first=Damon | last=Syson}}</ref>。預計建造兩艘的伊莉莎白女王級將會給予英國海軍遠較無敵級更相近美軍航艦的性能，提供資訊給[[英國下議院|下議院]][[英國國防委員會|國防委員會]]的[[第一海務大臣|第一海務大臣]]——[[艾倫·威斯特爵士|艾倫·威斯特爵士]]聲稱，與美國航艦協同作戰的能力為該航艦性能與噸位的決定性因素，「我曾與[[美國海軍作戰部長|海軍作戰部長]]交流過，他由衷希望我們有這樣的武力，並可與其航艦戰鬥群一同作戰，但在噸位排序上，他們希望能保有第一名的位置。<ref>[http://www.publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm200405/cmselect/cmdfence/45/4112404.htm House of Commons Minutes of Evidence]</ref>」

美國新一代的航艦為[[福特級航空母艦|福特級]]，亦是排水量十萬噸以上的超級航空母艦。

==替代品==
美國海軍目前擁有10艘這種軍艦，其在常規戰爭與非對稱戰鬥下的脆弱性，一直以來多少有改採用小型航艦改變現況的理念發聲，例如前作戰部長[[艾勒默·朱姆沃爾特|艾勒默·朱姆沃爾特]]（Elmo Zumwalt）提出的「[[制海艦|制海艦]]」構想<ref>[http://www.usni.org/magazines/proceedings/story.asp?STORY_ID=2164 Fortress at Sea? The Carrier Invulnerability Myth]</ref><ref>[http://www.military.com/features/0,15240,106292,00.html Lawmaker Calls for Study on Small Carriers]</ref>。然而，超級航空母艦仍被認為比小型航艦更具有成本效益<ref>[http://books.google.com/books?id=LC5HAAAAYAAJ Warbirds of the sea: a history of aircraft carriers & carrier-based aircraft, By Walter A. Musciano, Page 553]</ref>。制海艦構想雖然沒被美國海軍採納，但是設計概念輸出給西班牙、義大利等，搭配垂直起降戰機成為1970年代起西歐國家運用的[[輕型航空母艦|輕型航空母艦]]或[[兩棲突擊艦|兩棲突擊艦]]。

另外還有一種模組化、專作為海上基地、預計建造10艘的航艦概念—「移動式海上基地」（簡稱「MOB」），可不用借助盟國陸上基地作戰，但在2001年因為成本考量而放棄。

